<li id="cite_note-85"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-85">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">William Meacham, <i>The Authentication of the Turin Shroud: An Issue in Archaeological Epistemology</i>, Current Anthropology, Volume 24, No 3, June 1983</span>
