<li id="cite_note-Drake85-90"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Drake85_90-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Drake85_90-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Drake85_90-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Tim Drake, 2002, Saints of the Jubilee, <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-4033-1009-5" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-4033-1009-5">978-1-4033-1009-5</a> pp. 85–95</span>
