<li id="cite_note-Odell63-92"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Odell63_92-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Catherine M. Odell, 1998, Faustina: Apostle of Divine Mercy OSV Press <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-87973-923-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-87973-923-2">978-0-87973-923-2</a>  pp. 63–64</span>
